How to Reduce App Startup Time


✅ Move to background thread
Use coroutines
viewModelScope.launch {
    val data = withContext(Dispatchers.IO) {
        repository.loadFromDisk()
    }
}

✅ Use Lazy Initialization

val retrofit by lazy {
    createRetrofit()
}

✅ Reduce Layout Inflation Cost


Use ConstraintLayout efficiently
Use ViewStub for rarely used UI
Flatten hierarchy



✅ Defer Non-Critical SDKs

Big offenders:

Analytics
Crash reporting
Ads SDKs
✅ Strategy:
Initialize after first screen
Or use background thread


