Real banking scenario

👉 Expected answers:

Disable button
Use Mutex
Use debounce
Use StateFlow to control state


🔹 With Mutex ✅
private val mutex = Mutex()

suspend fun makePayment() {
    mutex.withLock {
        api.makePayment()
    }
}

